I've pretty much always focused on printing my own designs, usually for projects that are so One-Off that no one else would have any use for them, but recently I'm finding myself creating and remixing things Just Because I Can (and/or as a way to learn more about 3D modelling and 3D printing's applications in the rapid prototyping arena) so am hoping to start giving back to the community I've learned and benefited so much from.
